{"route":"/docs/reference/math/class/","title":"Class","description":"Documentation for the `class` function.","part":null,"outline":[{"id":"summary","name":"概要","children":[]},{"id":"例","name":"例","children":[]},{"id":"parameters","name":"引数","children":[{"id":"parameters-class","name":"class","children":[]},{"id":"parameters-body","name":"body","children":[]}]}],"body":{"kind":"func","content":{"path":["math"],"name":"class","title":"Class","keywords":[],"oneliner":"特定の数式クラスを強制的に適用。","element":true,"contextual":false,"deprecation":null,"details":"<p>特定の数式クラスを強制的に適用。</p>\n<p>これは、特定の記号を異なるクラスのように扱うのに便利です。例えば、ある記号を関係のように振る舞わせることができます。\n記号のクラスは、レイアウトのされ方、周囲の空白の入れ方、添え字がデフォルトでどのように取り付けられるかを定義します。\n添え字の取り付け方は<a href=\"/docs/reference/math/attach/#functions-limits\"><code>limits</code></a>や<a href=\"/docs/reference/math/attach/#functions-scripts\"><code>scripts</code></a>を使って常に上書きできることに注意してください。</p>\n<h2 id=\"例\">例</h2>\n<div class=\"previewed-code\"><pre><code><span class=\"typ-key\">#</span><span class=\"typ-key\">let</span> loves <span class=\"typ-op\">=</span> math<span class=\"typ-punct\">.</span><span class=\"typ-func\">class</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"typ-str\">&quot;relation&quot;</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">,</span>\n  sym<span class=\"typ-punct\">.</span>suit<span class=\"typ-punct\">.</span>heart<span class=\"typ-punct\">,</span>\n<span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"typ-math-delim\">$</span>x <span class=\"typ-pol\">loves</span> y <span class=\"typ-pol\">and</span> y <span class=\"typ-pol\">loves</span> 5<span class=\"typ-math-delim\">$</span>\n</code></pre><div class=\"preview\"><img src=\"/docs/assets/e3ed6eac7ab33197c87fb7cb4f0ff530.png\" alt=\"Preview\"></div></div>","example":null,"self":false,"params":[{"name":"class","details":"<p>コンテンツに適用するクラス。</p>","example":null,"types":["str"],"strings":[{"string":"normal","details":"<p>特別でない要素のデフォルトクラス。</p>"},{"string":"punctuation","details":"<p>カンマなどの句読点。</p>"},{"string":"opening","details":"<p><code>(</code>などの開き区切り文字。</p>"},{"string":"closing","details":"<p><code>)</code>などの閉じ区切り文字。</p>"},{"string":"fence","details":"<p><code>|</code>などの両側が同じ区切り文字。</p>"},{"string":"large","details":"<p><code>sum</code>のような大型演算子。</p>"},{"string":"relation","details":"<p><code>=</code>や<code>prec</code>のような関係記号。</p>"},{"string":"unary","details":"<p><code>not</code>のような単項演算子。</p>"},{"string":"binary","details":"<p><code>times</code>のような二項演算子。</p>"},{"string":"vary","details":"<p><code>+</code>のような単項にも二項にもなる演算子。</p>"}],"default":null,"positional":true,"named":false,"required":true,"variadic":false,"settable":false},{"name":"body","details":"<p>クラスを適用するコンテンツ。</p>","example":null,"types":["content"],"strings":[],"default":null,"positional":true,"named":false,"required":true,"variadic":false,"settable":false}],"returns":["content"],"scope":[]}}}